    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A grayish-white element with symbol As and atomic number 33, having a metallic luster, vaporizing when heated, and forming poisonous compounds. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
